Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.80,0:02:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,理由也不用多说吧
