Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且这一季的展开也没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有更好的方法的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家当然会去做别的选择了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也会那样做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.00,0:03:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你意思是说有比把我革职更好的方法?
