Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.50,0:03:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直以来我给过你足够的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在是抽身的时候了 今日子
