Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离开幕不到一个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我当然知道没有时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.70,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 「他」肯定地说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这季一定会赢得冠军给我们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,名云京志郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那位在我们面前保证这季会夺冠的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是你的继任人
