Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.40,0:04:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不到会有这样和你一起共事的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.70,0:04:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,命运的女神好像终于也注意我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是葵今日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然我是第一次和你见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你的事我很早就有所耳闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无意间失礼了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你变得很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且 我佩服你能努力到这地步
