Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你现在这样说让我觉得是在讽刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你别那样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.90,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也从祖父和爸爸那里听过许多关于你的传闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说你是最具才干而且平步青云的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.60,0:05:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因为目前为止我老是遇上好做的工作而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.00,0:05:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我真正的未来现在才要开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道现在高智能方程式的形势很严峻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.30,0:05:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我是第一次率领车队去比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有很多事一定要请你协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你敢保证会夺冠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但说话却很小心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定会夺冠的 绝对会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是为了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你会认为我明明是门外汉却在大言不惭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.60,0:06:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但如果没有这样的气势 如何能在胜负的世界里争雄?
