Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,C零件还有几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两套 要用吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.40,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成的NEW-X史培利昂 超乎预料的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.90,0:07:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这季绝对不能落后舒特洛杰和菅生车队的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然还要有人别下太荒唐的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你别那样刁难我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.00,0:07:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 你不是说你有你的想法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.80,0:07:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么 我想你很快就会知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.10,0:07:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.90,0:07:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么有个奇怪的家伙闯进车道来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎样?有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 今天的预定表里没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道那是你的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.30,0:08:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何 来个小比赛怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 三圈如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你到底在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然让训练安排里没有的车子进入车道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为他们全是职业车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.30,0:08:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.50,0:08:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你自豪的Ex-Superion不是在做最终调整了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是说 你害怕它会输吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.10,0:08:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的假的!?时速七百公里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们听好了 下次经过终点线后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跑三圈跟车子决一胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂 你突然间讲什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这又没有在预定中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说废话 快比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,输了的话 我不会饶了你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.10,0:09:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 我现在正在测试啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.40,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用再啰嗦了 这样才能看出有没有调整好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们要当作真正的比赛去跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁来记录一下时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管了 既然她都那么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,管它是哪来的赛车 我才不会输呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才你看见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像做了奇怪的变形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.80,0:09:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了?差距愈来愈大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.30,0:09:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了!我已经马力全开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.90,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1分11秒554
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比加贺的圈速记录快了两秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样子不用三圈就决出胜负了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为何有这样的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.00,0:10:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是说你的想法还太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能够获胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ex-Superion的开发就到今天为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.40,0:10:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不想在冠军杯上也遇到同样的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今日子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为再跑下去也是白跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白白弄坏车子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个速度跟我们的级别不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有胜算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.20,0:10:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那辆车子在这车道跑出的最好时间是1分10秒462
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且 那辆车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝不会因为操作错误而发生意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.60,0:10:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.10,0:11:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎内压上升 再加速会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请停车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会一直受人欺压的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条 车坏了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为不会再用那辆车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦你了 菲尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 刚来就惊吓了大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我想还是早点让你们看到的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,车名是 葵·AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是葵车队的跑车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但不是在工厂里制造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那究竟在哪里做出这部车的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.20,0:12:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成这部车的 是我的企划组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.60,0:12:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它所搭载的是生化计算机 AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.20,0:12:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,车身使用了稀有金属T3000
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生化计算机?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么稀有金属？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 果然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们看见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它的变形方式是过去所没有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点也没有拖沓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.90,0:12:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,融合这两种最尖端科技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.10,0:12:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是我的企划的主题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.20,0:12:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我本来没打算用来制造高智能方程式的跑车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.10,0:12:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 我接到社长的提议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说它最适合用在高智能方程式里的系统上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是 诞生了这部 AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爷爷他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从未跟我提起这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.00,0:13:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为当时还不知道会有什么结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是有了它 我们就能报一箭之仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以击败舒特洛杰和菅生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这季我会用这部AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿下冠军杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有异议吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.40,0:13:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他从开发阶段起就一直驾驶AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他叫菲尔·弗利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然没有参加大赛的经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但他是个很让人期待的新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条!没事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.80,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 老板 我把新车...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对啊 你不必在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我们不会用那辆车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且你被解雇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.00,0:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很遗憾 我的车队不需要他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这时候你胡说些什么话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在任何时候 不需要的东西就是不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会派菲尔和加贺参加冠军杯赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们才值得期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.10,0:14:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然想解雇经验丰富的新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而起用一个什么都不懂的新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种事我不同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛车不是经验丰富的人就能赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特别是他这种情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.80,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使是假设
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你这是对有拿过冠军的赛车手说的话吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说冠军？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那一年是没有什么人参赛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你认为那种冠军谁会认同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能说是暂时的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且他在心理方面有太多的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.30,0:14:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一激动起来就失去作为车手的冷静判断力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚刚不也是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.40,0:15:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺察觉到了极限而降低了车速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但他却意气用事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他就是这样才演出了在终点前用坏车子的丑态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.20,0:15:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺虽然没有冠军头衔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.50,0:15:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但谁都认同实力方面是加贺略胜一筹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.70,0:15:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前年和那个奇迹的世界冠军\N风见隼人演出了一幕惊人对决的也是加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说再用这个人有什么意义？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副社长!请你适可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.20,0:15:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这样庇护他、宠他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果等于害了他自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不忍心解雇赢不了比赛车手的老板是个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但赢不了比赛的车手问题更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.70,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之今天上演的开除戏就是这道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你别胡说好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这与那是两回事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.10,0:15:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白你宠爱自己培养的赛车手的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.60,0:16:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 对那种抱着天塌下来也有人挡着的心态的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,期待他有好结果是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而你这样宠溺他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就会使他更加无能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太过分!你在胡说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.90,0:16:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许我说得的确残酷了点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是把话挑明对彼此都有益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.20,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定会把胜利的荣耀献给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.90,0:16:44.70,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}迷路の出口どこなのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.70,0:16:48.40,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}誰も知らずに走ってる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.40,0:16:55.60,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}ほんとうはすぐそこにあっても气がつかずに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.90,0:16:59.30,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}梦破れてもはぐれてもやり直せるよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赢不了比赛的车手问题更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.70,0:17:07.00,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}何もかも振り出しまで唳ったとしても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.00,0:17:10.40,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}あなたの輝き
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.80,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}強くなる度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.80,0:17:18.07,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}私のこと變えてゆく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.90,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}倒れそうなとき 思い出してね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.90,0:17:29.50,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}あなたは今ひとりきりじゃないこと Believe！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.70,0:17:37.20,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}そばにいても離れててもどこにいてもずっと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.70,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}同じ空に羽ばたいてる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:49.60,Sonjap,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\a6}私がいることいつも感じてて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.30,0:17:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条!你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你振作起来了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是有点憔悴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心情多少有点影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是作为车手现在才开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.60,0:18:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此 我想问你一些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想问别人的意见 礼物就只有那些吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早料到你会这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.10,0:18:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是想听我的意见吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然还是要用到这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美国?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.10,0:18:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 我想试着去突破过去到现在的瓶颈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要去那个赛车之国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.80,0:18:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,参加卡车大赛或是普通型赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.90,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 我想拼命参加各种不同的比赛磨练自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.80,0:18:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为新社长的话也有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的确是很天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对车队是 对老板也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是什么常败的车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我说的不是那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 我缺乏某种东西的确是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我要去美国把它找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我考虑许久得出的结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.40,0:19:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这倒是不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以你这个模范生来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为这是个好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你去过那里后应该会变得更大胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.10,0:19:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你跟美琪说了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.30,0:19:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有 我现在没脸见她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我老在她面前出丑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.40,0:19:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确实是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.90,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安定下来后我会和她联系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那里玩赛车的情况是怎样的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我在那边朋友的地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么事就试着去找他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们看起来很凶险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但全是很讲义气的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.00,0:20:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.65,0:20:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{}美国 曼哈顿岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,城之内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.90,0:21:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是 还要我这样为你担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.50,0:21:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然不先找我就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊...那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,城之内...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,44号登机口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.70,0:21:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.10,0:21:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是为了做你的技师来葵车队的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.80,0:21:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有你 我留在那里没什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想去美国玩赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就替你去维修车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.90,0:21:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是这样决定的 就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,城之内...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.80,0:21:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 情况不是任何时候都那么乐观的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.80,0:21:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今年对我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在某方面来说情况是很险峻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.10,0:22:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我对花环没有任何顾忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它是一部拥有优秀性能的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.10,0:22:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也使用它相当一段时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.20,0:22:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 不只比赛整体的方向性在逐渐改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连车子也一样在变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.50,0:22:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那种形势里能发挥怎样的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我所在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.70,0:22:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你接受采访 祝你好运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.90,0:22:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.50,0:22:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风见先生还是那么酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.40,0:22:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 这一季我要好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.00,0:22:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还在说呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.50,0:22:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香小姐不在 现在是大好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.20,0:22:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要用这锻炼出来的好身材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.70,0:22:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把风见先生迷死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.60,0:22:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去年也听过你相同的台词呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.00,0:22:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.50,0:22:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那胸围跟明日香比起来还早得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.30,0:22:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.50,0:22:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 菅生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.60,0:22:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.20,0:22:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不...我还不习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.40,0:22:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的新脸孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.50,0:23:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说新脸孔真是失礼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要说变回原来的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.60,0:23:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了 我来介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.60,0:23:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的新人 雷欧·安哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.90,0:23:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.00,0:23:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那算什么问候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.60,0:23:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要更有礼貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.70,0:23:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是菅生修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.10,0:23:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是...雷欧·安哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.50,0:23:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好 雷欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.70,0:23:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你终于当教官了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.70,0:23:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也难怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的年纪是最大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我还不至于会输给这些菜鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.20,0:23:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这小子年纪和风见一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却轻浮得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.80,0:23:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这跟赛车完全没有关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.70,0:23:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看似没有其实有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.10,0:23:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 这小子和葵车队的新人是同期的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.20,0:23:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那斯卡时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.00,0:23:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于要到了新人的时代了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.50,0:23:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别挡住晚辈的路哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.90,0:23:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.00,0:24:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葵的新人 菲尔·弗利兹吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.50,0:24:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,预赛开始经过30分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.90,0:24:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,顶尖车队陆续在向极速挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暂定的最优先起跑位置是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.20,0:24:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚开始就跑出1分37秒266
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.50,0:24:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舒特洛杰的合作伙伴杰奇·古德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.90,0:24:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有谁能突破这个纪录呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.40,0:24:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风见隼人现在通过控制线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.50,0:24:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厉害 厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.80,0:24:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经被超越了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.60,0:24:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我说你是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.10,0:24:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厉害的人现在才开始跑出全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.60,0:24:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而你却把轮胎用光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.20,0:24:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有就是本季进行大改革
